definition: to hang or suspend/to worry/public announcement/unresolved/baseless/without foundation

sentences.english: The heavy build of the EXE cantilever-bed lathe is evident from this picture.
sentences.chinese: 沉重的EXE文件建立悬臂梁床车床于此可见图片。

sentences.english: He modeled a tree as cantilevered beams assembled to form a fractal network.
sentences.chinese: 他将树木当作悬臂结构来建模，并形成一个分形网络。

sentences.english: A simple control strategy is presented for a smart cantalever structure with piezoelectricity.
sentences.chinese: 该文提出了一种简单的悬臂板压电智能结构控制策略。

sentences.english: High speed decoiler with cantilever support, adopting ground recoiling reduces the heavy labor of excavating a pit.
sentences.chinese: 采用高速悬臂开卷，地面放卷，减少开挖地坑之苦。

sentences.english: This article presents a reconstruction project, which is mainly on how to control the noise of single stage hanging-arm centrifugal blower.
sentences.chinese: 介绍一例单级悬臂离心风机噪声综合治理工程。

sentences.english: Vibrations of Timoshenko beam per unit disturbance are investigated in theory.
sentences.chinese: 理论上研究了单位力扰动下的悬臂梁的振动。

sentences.english: Fourbar linkage & double cantilever flat flap gate is a new type of structure on water conservancy project.
sentences.chinese: 四联杆双悬臂平面翻板闸是一种新型水工建筑物。

sentences.english: The pulley moves in straight line along the I-shape steel and rotates along the swing arm.
sentences.chinese: 葫芦沿工字钢作直线运动和悬臂作旋转运动。

sentences.english: The balcony of the living-room is cantilevered.
sentences.chinese: 起居室的阳台是用悬臂支撑的。

sentences.english: In this paper we have designed and fabricated the ultra-sensitive cantilevers for single electron spin detection.
sentences.chinese: 提出一种用于单电子自旋探测微悬臂梁的制作方法。

sentences.english: An area of welcome shade is naturally created by the cantilevered structure.
sentences.chinese: 一个欢迎阴影面积，自然创造的悬臂式结构。

sentences.english: A solution viscosity measurement technique using a resonating microcantilever is proposed.
sentences.chinese: 提出了一种测量溶液粘度的微悬臂梁谐振技术。

sentences.english: The micro-cantilever has two kinds of working mode, namely deflection mode and resonance frequency mode.
sentences.chinese: 微悬臂梁有两种工作模式，即弯曲模式和共振模式。

sentences.english: Less prominent arms are mostly gas and star nurseries.
sentences.chinese: 不太突出的悬臂大部分是气体和星星滋生地。

sentences.english: Art piece-like staircase in cantilevered steel frame is situated behind the entrance door.
sentences.chinese: 艺术楼梯采用悬臂式钢结构，位于入口大门的后面。

sentences.english: In his design the beam cantilevers out too far for balance.
sentences.chinese: 在他的设计中，悬臂梁伸出太多，不能平衡。
